{"tid":563970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"終於可以直接支持Wintergatan...","createTime":"2018-02-17T12:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T13:50:02.000Z","uid":138409,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"83ce331ac3b79b6a1dd16d317b516ce7fc3a17de","tid":563970,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T12:49:15.000Z","msg":"入正題之前首先有無人聽過／知道Wintergatan呢對band<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果無，容許我吹奏下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有就skip it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【吹奏開始】<br />\n一直以來都覺得Wintergatan呢支band好正<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/202940_72acded3acd45e4c8b6ed680854b8ab1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F202940_72acded3acd45e4c8b6ed680854b8ab1.jpg&h=7f912419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為他們的曲風合我口味（類似鋼片琴／音樂盒之類...tranquilizing的音樂風格），<br />\n而且極有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（例如以下呢段音樂，將木鋸當小提琴拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2xgWuw3TOJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2xgWuw3TOJA&d=u16ti%2BQKRfEP63qtE5Xr1ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=bb93b806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2xgWuw3TOJA</a><br />\n寫完音樂仲要任人免費download，不設paywall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次down完都有點過意不去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最勁係明明玩音樂，結果連mechanical engineering都玩埋<br />\n之前整過部Marble Machine<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvUU8joBb1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIvUU8joBb1Q&d=u16ti%2BQKRfEP63qtE5Xr1ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=472448b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvUU8joBb1Q</a><br />\n<br />\n現在整緊部升級版- Marble Machine X<br />\n(每個部件的製作過程都公開，而且會在留言區收集意見改良設計，crowdsourcing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLLLYkE3G1HED6rW-bkliHbMroHYFf4ukv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLLLYkE3G1HED6rW-bkliHbMroHYFf4ukv&d=u16ti%2BQKRfEP63qtE5Xr1ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2d77a0ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLLLYkE3G1HED6rW-bkliHbMroHYFf4ukv</a><br />\n依家他們的目標是帶著Marble Machine X進行巡迴演出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望會來香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n【吹奏完畢】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一直以來有follow開他們的channel，最近得知他們用了YouTube的Sponsor功能<br />\n即刻狗衝落樓下7仔增值Google play account<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/202902_3577cafd24b979fb8b8e0e8b1ab813eb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F202902_3577cafd24b979fb8b8e0e8b1ab813eb.JPG&h=defbcecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每月捐$25，捐得過啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/203224_df29e5daf881406663297a47cb9fd116.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F203224_df29e5daf881406663297a47cb9fd116.png&h=d2666743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以本文重點是<br />\n<br />\n1. 見到外國Youtuber如此犀利，再望望香港哥班，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. Youtuber廣告收入逐漸減少未嘗不是好事，至少單靠clickbait騙流量班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而有能力、質素頂尖哥班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 純粹想推廣Wintergatan，令更多人認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c56ee52d435dea4588eda9be6449b04044a5647","tid":563970,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a46af4e14b43cdeea352f774badfbc46955043c","tid":563970,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a73ce921cc447a6094e653cc65917acfb0ead0e9","tid":563970,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"05961c84f10d7abc25a80e9f33e4b73912cd7b01","tid":563970,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:08:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b8117520b22ca4a65109e818aec0112ee3295b1d","tid":563970,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:12:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9f55266c8d510c7c435471ce453a32554d0be3c3","tid":563970,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb24bd6a3e19244e1f99086651d74ad40382c9ff","tid":563970,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:15:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ef01c57e0c69af5a60e17e601ebe94f1796c14fa","tid":563970,"uid":79164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:50:02.000Z","msg":"支持 有追開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}